messages.title: MAKING BREXIT A SUCCESS IS CENTRAL TO OUR NATIONAL INTEREST
messages.content: With a strong negotiating hand in Europe, Theresa May can guarantee our economic security and build a stronger, fairer Britain in charge of its own future.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Ensure a successful Brexit to guarantee our economic security and a stronger, fairer Britain.
With Theresa May's leadership, the Conservatives will deliver economic stability and a secure future.

issues.brexitEurope: With a strong negotiating hand in Europe, Theresa May can guarantee our economic security and build a stronger, fairer Britain in charge of its own future.
issues.economy: With your help and your vote for Mary Macleod as your local Conservative MP, we can guarantee economic security and a secure future.
